jobs:
  build:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - name: Checkout code
        uses: actions/checkout@v3

      - name: Run echo
        run: echo "Hello DevOps!"

ğŸŸ¡ YAML uses spaces (not tabs). Indentation matters a lot.


